  <brief_title>Stereotactic Radiosurgery and Radiation Therapy in Treating Patients With Glioblastoma Multiforme</brief_title>
  <official_title>Phase II Trial of Conventional Radiotherapy With Stereotactic Radiosurgery to High Risk Tumor Regions as Determined by Functional Imaging in Patients With Glioblastoma Multiforme</official_title>
